vendors.name: Wagner Family Farm
vendors.description: Always an avid gardener, Chris Wagner spent years expanding a small plot in the family's suburban home. Each year, the yield of fruits and vegetables grew & recipes for sauce, jellies, and more were perfected. In 2021, the time was finally right to transition from gardener to farmer, and Wagner Family Farms was born.

vendors.description: This Organic Farm follows organic and regenerative farming practices, growing a variety of fruits and vegetables. In addition to producing, they keep pastured raised chickens for eggs, a small herd of rescue animals, honey bees for pollination and honey production, and gourmet mushrooms.
